SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Constanza  Ferreiro
AuthorCountry: Argentina
Text: "To my dearest,\n\nI dont really know you Well, but I think i've know you for\
  \ decades.\nJust three days with you in a cold march were enough to know you \xE1\
  re the one for me.\n\nYou left me without Air, pumped up my feelings, and all that\
  \ was only after I get to knew a little part of your old soul.\n\nBeautiful Portugal,\
  \ I just got the pleausure to see you from de hights, but i want to know you and\
  \ go further, i know we can.\n\nLet me fall for you even more.\n\nWith all my love\
  \ from Argentina\n\nConnie"
